message.content: Jay stood irresolute for a moment, half decided to go back and join Lilygar and Doc, while she wanted to do no more than run upstairs to her room, promising that Gavin Aalborg, who he had told her that he loved her, was already flirting with a girl that he had only met a few minutes before.
